<HL>
   Student Loan Guarantors End Talks
   For Merger, Citing Federal Opposition
   ----
   By Gary Putka
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
07/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A3
</SO>
